 29/8 /18 Herbecourt ourselv in the old Isolat fever ward . From this place we see a high ridg cover with wood about 5 kilo away and take a sharp right angl turn this is the far bank of the River Somm and at the foot of the portion direct to our front is the town of Peronn . The enemi is hold this and the other side of the villag strong and prevent our cross . The 23rd have some of their compani in old YMCAs which adjoin here but as Fritz was use a high veloc gun with good effect close to here I issu order for all my chap to be in trench and am shift out myself . Tonight the men get a hot meal and a meat supper and draw their greatcoat for the night . No word of an immedi move .
